### Variables
@baseUrl = https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Envoyer un message (cas nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages/send-message
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipient_id": "recipient-uuid-here",
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "subject": "Question sur l'événement",
  "content": "Bonjour, j'aimerais avoir plus d'informations sur l'événement."
}

### Test 2 - Envoyer un message sans sujet
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages/send-message
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipient_id": "recipient-uuid-here",
  "content": "Message simple sans sujet"
}

### Test 3 - Erreur: recipient_id manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages/send-message
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Message sans destinataire"
}

### Test 4 - Erreur: content manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages/send-message
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipient_id": "recipient-uuid-here"
}

### Test 5 - Erreur: destinataire inexistant
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages/send-message
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipient_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "content": "Message"
}

